description: Algo description: Loop over a given <array: number[]> and check if current element array[i] is greater than array[i + 1]. If true, Swap the elements. Instructions: In this app, numbers can repeat many times. The more you set <Array length> without raising <Max numbers>, the greater is the amount of times that numbers repeat themselves. There is no maximum number that you can set as the <Array length>, so very large numbers can crash your page. Check the Worst case on Time complexity.
